<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sindika Storage API - Manajemen Dokumen Gereja</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        
        @keyframes shimmer {
            0% { background-position: -1000px 0; }
            100% { background-position: 1000px 0; }
        }
        
        .float-animation {
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        .fade-in-up {
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
        }
        
        .feature-card {
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        }
        
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        
        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 50%, #047857 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        
        .ai-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #6366f1 50%, #3b82f6 100%);
        }
        
        .shimmer {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent);
            background-size: 1000px 100%;
            animation: shimmer 3s infinite;
        }
        
        .glow {
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
        }
        
        .ai-glow {
            box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4);
        }
        
        .icon-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .icon-wrapper::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 0;
            height: 0;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            transition: width 0.6s, height 0.6s;
        }
        
        .feature-card:hover .icon-wrapper::before {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
        }
        
        .glass-morphism {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(30px) saturate(180%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-emerald-50 to-teal-50 min-h-screen">
     <%- include('partials/_navbar') %>

    <main class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pt-32 pb-20">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in-up">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 rounded-3xl mb-8 glow float-animation">
                <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 19a2 2 0 01-2-2V7a2 2 0 012-2h4l2 2h4a2 2 0 012 2v1M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2v-5a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v5a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">Storage API</h1>
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold gradient-text mb-8">Pusat Dokumen Gereja yang Aman & Cerdas</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Kelola semua dokumen penting gereja Anda dengan aman dan cerdas. Dari notulensi majelis, laporan keuangan, hingga materi pembinaan jemaat‚Äîsemuanya tersimpan terpusat, terorganisir, dan dibantu oleh AI.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- AI Assistant Feature - Hero -->
        <div class="mb-16 p-10 glass-morphism rounded-3xl shadow-2xl ai-glow fade-in-up relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 ai-gradient rounded-full filter blur-3xl opacity-20"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 rounded-full filter blur-3xl opacity-20"></div>
            
            <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
                <div class="w-24 h-24 ai-gradient rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-xl">
                    <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">AI-Powered Intelligent File Assistant</h3>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-4">Asisten AI yang memahami konteks gereja Anda. Temukan dokumen dengan bahasa natural, dapatkan ringkasan instan, dan ekstrak informasi penting hanya dengan bertanya.</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center md:justify-start">
                        <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 rounded-xl font-medium text-sm">üîç Pencarian Cerdas</span>
                        <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-xl font-medium text-sm">üìù Ringkasan Otomatis</span>
                        <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 rounded-xl font-medium text-sm">üí° Rekomendasi Dokumen</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-16">
            <div class="feature-card p-10 glass-morphism rounded-3xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl">
                <div class="icon-wrapper w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 rounded-2xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 7v10a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2h-6l-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">Organisasi Dokumen Rapi</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">Pisahkan dokumen berdasarkan kategori: notulensi majelis, laporan keuangan, materi katekisasi, surat keputusan, dan arsip sejarah gereja‚Äîsemua terstruktur dengan rapi.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card p-10 glass-morphism rounded-3xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl">
                <div class="icon-wrapper w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 rounded-2xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">Akses Berbasis Peran</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">Kontrol siapa yang bisa melihat apa. Majelis akses penuh, komisi lihat dokumen pelayanan mereka, jemaat akses materi umum‚Äîsemuanya teratur dan aman.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card p-10 glass-morphism rounded-3xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl">
                <div class="icon-wrapper w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 rounded-2xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">Riwayat & Versi Dokumen</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">Lacak setiap perubahan dokumen penting. Siapa yang upload, kapan direvisi, dan akses versi sebelumnya‚Äîtransparansi penuh untuk akuntabilitas gereja.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card p-10 glass-morphism rounded-3xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl">
                <div class="icon-wrapper w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-orange-600 rounded-2xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">Backup Otomatis</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">Dokumen penting gereja tidak akan pernah hilang. Sistem backup otomatis menjaga sejarah dan arsip gereja tetap aman untuk generasi mendatang.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- AI Features Grid -->
        <div class="mt-16 p-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 via-blue-500 to-indigo-500 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-10">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-slate-900 mb-10">Kecerdasan AI untuk Manajemen Dokumen</h3>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <div class="text-center p-6">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 ai-gradient rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Pencarian Natural</h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">"Cari notulen rapat majelis bulan Januari yang membahas anggaran"</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center p-6">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 ai-gradient rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Ekstraksi Informasi</h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">Ambil data penting dari dokumen panjang dalam hitungan detik</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center p-6">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 ai-gradient rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 8h10M7 12h4m1 8l-4-4H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-3l-4 4z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Tanya Dokumen</h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">Ajukan pertanyaan langsung tentang isi dokumen, dapatkan jawaban instan</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-20 p-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 via-teal-500 to-emerald-600 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl text-white text-center relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full shimmer"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
                <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Akhiri Era Dokumen Berantakan</h3>
                <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-emerald-50 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">Tidak perlu lagi mencari dokumen di lemari arsip atau email. Semua dokumen gereja ada di satu tempat yang aman, mudah diakses, dan dilengkapi asisten AI yang siap membantu.</p>
                <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center px-10 py-5 bg-white text-emerald-600 font-bold text-lg rounded-2xl shadow-2xl hover:shadow-3xl hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
                    Mulai Kelola Dokumen Gereja
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 ml-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>